### GPU Monitoring Not Working

Ensure NVIDIA GPU Operator is installed:
```bash
kubectl get pods -n gpu-operator
```

Check DCGM exporter:
```bash
kubectl get pods -n gpu-operator -l app=nvidia-dcgm-exporter
```

### Permission Issues

Verify service account permissions:
```bash
kubectl get serviceaccounts -n {{ .Script.Namespace }}
kubectl describe clusterrole nvsentinel
```

### MongoDB Connection Issues

If MongoDB is enabled, check connectivity:
```bash
kubectl get pods -n {{ .Script.Namespace }} -l app=mongodb
kubectl logs -n {{ .Script.Namespace }} -l app=platform-connectors
```

